Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.22,1:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, report to your nearest{\i0}\N{\i1}marked shuttle station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.55,1:11:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Planet evacuation in progress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.77,1:11:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, report to your nearest{\i0}\N{\i1}marked shuttle station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.19,1:11:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Planet evacuation in progress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.03,1:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, report to your nearest{\i0}\N{\i1}marked shuttle station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.45,1:11:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Planet evacuation in progress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.24,1:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All units, report to your nearest{\i0}\N{\i1}marked shuttle station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.66,1:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Planet evacuation in progress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.25,1:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweep's clean, no humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.71,1:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone fall out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.21,1:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Head back to your posts.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.59,1:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[Peter] That's gotta be the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.22,1:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.18,1:11:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Never trust a human to just let things be.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.02,1:11:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us are gonna have to stay ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.89,1:12:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you back at the factory.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.44,1:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.07,1:12:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.82,1:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.08,1:12:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.54,1:12:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whoa.\N-Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.55,1:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Hanna] Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.93,1:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.27,1:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.23,1:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We're the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.52,1:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.87,1:12:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.16,1:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's okay. Give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.50,1:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.00,1:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.67,1:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.00,1:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.72,1:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys here alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.05,1:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They killed Mom and Dad\Nbecause they were human.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.83,1:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[woman] You'll no longer\Nhave to live in fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.12,1:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories of the past will be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.58,1:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will be a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.91,1:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Peter] Alice. [human] Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.17,1:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The cord's the only thing\Nkeeping her alive right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.79,1:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, she's...\Nshe's breathing better, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.92,1:15:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's good.\N-Wouldn't call it "breathing."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.23,1:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.31,1:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long\Nit'll hold up, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.69,1:15:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.03,1:15:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.95,1:15:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the-- the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.12,1:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys tried to wipe us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.67,1:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We chose to forget. Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.00,1:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,picking what memories you can keep.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.26,1:16:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans don't have that luxury.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.23,1:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you helping us?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.90,1:16:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have killed us\Nwhen I was passed out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.61,1:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my grandparents\Nyou chased off the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.32,1:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even born yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.74,1:16:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.46,1:16:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been living in colonies{\i0}\N{\i1}on Mars since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.75,1:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}None of us had even been to Earth before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.88,1:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We didn't know what to expect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.84,1:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't even know{\i0}\N{\i1}if we could still breathe down here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.01,1:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We did learn everything about you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.72,1:16:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the synthetics.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.64,1:16:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How you drove us from our homes{\i0}\N{\i1}and left us with nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.15,1:16:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It took us all this time just to gather{\i0}\N{\i1}the resources we needed to come back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.61,1:17:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They told us you were monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.12,1:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Savages.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.37,1:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's kind of just one side of the story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.96,1:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.55,1:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why am I helping you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.64,1:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cause no one said{\i0}\N{\i1}I'd be coming down here killing kids...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.72,1:17:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and families.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.52,1:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not what I signed up for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.92,1:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.71,1:18:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby! Baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.71,1:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, you're doing well.\N-I saw...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.05,1:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw... I--I saw...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.26,1:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw... I...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.01,1:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dreams... it's the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.81,1:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our past.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.19,1:18:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-The dreams.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.65,1:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls... the girls!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.36,1:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, they're waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.86,1:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[man over PA]\N{\i1}Planet evacuation in progress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.32,1:18:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed to the platform{\i0}\N{\i1}in an orderly fashion, please,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.28,1:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and board the train.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.66,1:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[man continues indistinctly over PA]
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.12,1:18:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.20,1:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as David gets here,\Nwe're gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.08,1:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Last train!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.00,1:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.33,1:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Lucy, come on.\N-Not without Mommy and Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.88,1:18:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on.\N-They'll be here!{\i1} {\i0}Daddy said that!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.98,1:18:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[man over PA] {\i1}This is a Level Three{\i0}\N{\i1}mandatory evacuation.{\i0}
