Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.04,1:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. You know what? Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.00,1:20:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was never mine to begin with,\Nbut thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.54,1:20:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.54,1:20:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.46,1:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stay tight and low.\NCover, now! Go, go, go!
